      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Payment processing costs HVAC companies an average of $847 per month in fees, but choosing the wrong processor can increase that by 40%. After analyzing transaction data from 280+ HVAC contractors, we found companies using integrated payment solutions collect payments 23% faster and reduce processing costs by an average of $156 monthly.</p>

        <p>The payment processing landscape has shifted dramatically for HVAC companies. While traditional processors like Square and Stripe remain viable options, integrated solutions from <a href="https://go.getjobber.com/bo42cjptz4m2" rel="sponsored nofollow">Jobber</a> and <a href="https://housecallpro.partnerlinks.io/auy5xcz257sw" rel="sponsored nofollow">Housecall Pro</a> now offer competitive rates with seamless workflow integration that eliminates the 18-minute average delay between job completion and payment collection.</p>
