        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <p>Administrative labor costs assume $20/hour for payment reconciliation, invoice matching, and customer follow-up. Integrated solutions reduce these tasks by 75-85%, making them cost-effective even with slightly higher processing rates. Companies with dedicated administrative staff may find traditional merchants more economical for high-volume processing.</p>
